---
title: Plant-Based Protein Shreds and Corn Chowder with Green Onions
description: This chowder is made for chilly winter nights—and it's calling your name! Protein shreds and corn are the stars of the show in this big bowl of goodness, while a touch of jalapeño kicks up the flavour. Time to get cozy!
